  "original_title": "\u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel crisis continues due to adjourned Cabinet meeting",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The postponement of the cabinet meeting scheduled for Monday evening on the 11th due to President Gotabaya Rajapaksa's non-conciliation has intensified the fuel crisis facing the country.",
        "Therefore, a letter has been submitted by the Minister of Electricity and Power during the party leaders' meeting held on the evening of 11th.",
        "Through this, domestic banks will be allowed to raise 128 million dollars from the financial market as per the recommendations of the central bank and finance ministry.",
        "Therefore, after the appointment of the new government, the party leaders were requested to give an assurance that they will not object to the urgent purchase of fuel considering the current situation.",
        "However, some including Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa rejected it and stated that he cannot give any guarantee without the approval of the Cabinet. It is noteworthy that the effort to raise funds for the emergency purchase was suspended because of it."
      ],
